          "Offsets": [
            16,
            280,
            52,
            190
          ],
          "text": "A DECK is a document - like a HyperCard stack.\n\nIt contains an ordered list of CARDS, exactly one of which is shown at a time.\n\nEach card carries WIDGETS: buttons, text fields, shapes, pictures - and fully custom widgets you define yourself.\n\nEvery deck, card and widget has its own script.",
